data.enText: like sb/sth but not exactly the same

data.chText: 我的教学风格和多数教师相似。
data.enText: My teaching style is similar to that of most other teachers.
The two houses are similar in size.

data.chText: 我们所有的病人问题大致相似。
data.enText: All our patients have broadly similar problems.

simple_means.memory_skill: simil 相类似，一样 + ar …的 → 同样的；相似的

ex.chText: 从整体来看，这两幢楼是相似的。
ex.enText: The two buildings are similar on the whole.

ex.chText: 这对孪生兄弟在各方面都很像。
ex.enText: The twin brothers are similar in every respect.

synonyms.bx: 指不同的人或事物之间部分相似但不完全相同的，暗含可暂不考虑或忽略其差异之意。

ex.chText: 这两对夫妻的经济状况差不多。
ex.enText: The two couples are in a comparable financial situation.

ex.chText: 类似的香水在国外价格要高得多。
ex.enText: Comparable perfumes would cost far more abroad.

ex.chText: 鸟的翅膀与鱼的鳍功能相似。
ex.enText: A bird's wings are comparable in function to a fish's fins.

synonyms.bx: 指在大小、数量、价值、能力等方面有相似之处的，可作有限或粗略的对比。

ex.chText: 这就是我们去年住过的旅馆。
ex.enText: This is the identical hotel we stayed at last year.

ex.chText: 他的眼镜和我的完全一样。
ex.enText: His glasses are identical to/with mine.

ex.chText: 这两种说法实际上一模一样。
ex.enText: The two expressions are, in effect, identical.

synonyms.bx: 语气最强，可用于强调同一个人或事物，也可指数个人或事物之间完全没有差别的。

synonym.guide: 导航词义：相似的，类似的

tr: having the same or some of the same characteristics
example: a limited circle of like minds
members of the cat family have like dispositions
as like as two peas in a pod

tr: having the same or similar characteristics
example: friends are generally alike in background and taste

tr: capable of replacing or changing places with something else
permitting mutual substitution without loss of function or suitability

value.def: If one thing is similar to another, or if two things are similar, they have features that are the same.

example.ex: ...a savoury cake with a texture similar to that of carrot cake...
example.tran: 口感和胡萝卜蛋糕相似的一种美味蛋糕

example.ex: The accident was similar to one that happened in 1973.
example.tran: 这次事故和 1973 年发生的那起事故很相似。

trans: 相似形；相似圖形；相似图形；图形称为相似图形
有类似商品要卖；出售类似物品

rootsaffixes.indicate: = alike, same 相类似, 一样
rootsaffixes.title: simil, simul(t), sembl

simult 相类似，一样 + aneity 表性质 → 同时性
